references: Related: Ord 65076, Ord 65077, Ord 65166, Ord 62995. Amending: Ord 65386
summary: An ordinance relating to the acquisition of rights of way for 54th Avenue South as authorized under Ordinance No. 65076; for Beacon Avenue as authorized under Ordinance No. 65077, as amended by Ordinance No. 65166; and for certain arterial highway corners as contemplated by Ordinance No. 62995; and amending Section 1 of Ordinance No. 65386, which appropriates money therefor.
